# Raw design-source & print-resolution files.
# These get converted to lightweight web assets (.glb, .png/.jpg, compressed PDF)
# which ARE committed — the heavy originals stay local only.
*.skp
*.dae
*.obj
*.mtl
*.fbx
*.3ds
*.dwg
*.max

# Big raw PDFs: commit only compressed web derivatives (suffix -web.pdf)
*.pdf
!*-web.pdf

# OS cruft
Thumbs.db
.DS_Store
